      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. When you mention the \"clashes\" and the mistrust, does that generally manifest as actual widespread violence or more like constant tribal instability? I'm trying to gauge if the whole region is basically a powder keg where any small ethnic disagreement could spark a bigger conflict.",
